subject: AW: [junit] RPM available for junit
msgSnippet: I don t think so. But you can register to monitor the project on http://sourceforge.net/projects/junit/ for this purpose. ... Von: David Roussel
messageBody:
I don't think so. But you can register to monitor the project on http://sourceforge.net/projects/junit/ for this purpose.
-----Ursprüngliche Nachricht-----
Von: David Roussel [mailto:dir@...]
Gesendet: Donnerstag, 7. Juni 2001 12:16
An: junit@yahoogroups.com
Betreff: RE: [junit] RPM available for junit

Do normal Junit releases get notified here?  I don't recall seeing any.
-----Original Message-----
From: gomez_henri@... [mailto:gomez_henri@...]
Sent: 07 June 2001 11:15
To: junit@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [junit] RPM available for junit

Hi to all,

A quick note to inform RPM users, that
Junit 3.7 RPM are available at :

ftp://ftp.falsehope.com/home/gomez/junit/

Next to RPMs for jakarta.apache.org and xml.apache.org
projects :)

Regards.
